snippet.title: Wunderling - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Nintendo Switch and PC early 2020.
Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/732930/Wunderling

Take control of the Wunderling, a low-level video game goon who has just unlocked the power to jump. Unable to stop or change direction at will, you will need to plan ahead and master the Wunderlings’ abilities to navigate treacherous scrolling levels and chase down that pesky Hero.

Twitter: https://twitter.com/retroidofficial
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/retroidinteractive
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/retroidinteractive/
Discord: https://discord.gg/g9SRVXN
Web: https://retroid.com
